basic and simple database for company using php and mysql
created for modul 3 assignment

index.php: the main page if we open the web program. you can add your data there
connection.php: this file use to call the database from mysql into the program
insert.php: used as the back end of the index.php. this program use as back-end for index.php so that you can input your data into the index.php
view.php: used as the "visualization of your data in the database.
delete.php: functioned so you can delete your data directly from the view.php
edit.php: functioned so you can change your data in database
update.php: functioned so you can possibly update the data from edit.php
